No hay fever, sinus trouble Mouth and Throat: Last to dentist 2 yr ago. Occasional canker sore Neck: No lumps, goiter, pain Breasts: No lumps, pain, discharge. Habits: Patient claims to have quit smoking about two years ago. FAMILY HISTORY - Mother died, 67, stroke; had varicose veins, headaches, hypertension - Father died, 43, train accident
